The AllAfrica Media Group will celebrate International Women's Day this year with a high-profile event in Rabat, Morocco from March 7 to 9. The AllAfrica Women's Agenda Forum (AWA 2023) will spotlight the role of women in securing the continent's food resources and in combating poverty. AllAfrica Global Media is also jointly announcing with the PhilJohn Academy scholarships for 60 young women from 18 countries who will receive training in leadership, entrepreneurship and technology.